/**
 * GENERATED — do not hand-edit. Run the thumbnail script if the images change.
 *
 * The OG share card renders on the edge runtime: it cannot read the filesystem,
 * and it must not fetch over the network, because an unfurl that depends on a
 * round-trip is an unfurl that intermittently fails. So the portraits and
 * product shots it draws are inlined here as 96-112px data URIs (~290 KB total).
 *
 * These are ONLY for the OG card. Everything in the browser loads the real
 * images from /public.
 */

